    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "«ЧАО\nRABAUL\nFINSCHAFEI\nLAE\nPORT MORESBY\nNew Guinea\nBIRD OF PARADISE SERVICE\nand Islands Services\nNOUMEA - SUVA\n- VILA - ESPIRITU SANTO\nNORFOLK ISLAND\nLORD HOWE ISLAND\nThe Qantas New Guinea Service (known as\nthe\n\"Bird\nof Paradise\"\nService)\nleaves\nSydney three times weekly.\nTwo of these\nservices terminate at Lae, and the third goes\non to Rabaul.\nPassengers are also carried\nto and from North Queensland ports.\nA Qantas air service links Noumea and Suva\nwith Sydney. From Noumea a service extends\nto Vila and Espiritu Santo.\nA Norfolk Island service is flown by speedy\nLancastrian\naircraft\nevery\nfortnight from\nSydney, and a charter service is flown by a\nQantas\nCatalina between Sydney and Lord\nHowe Island once weekly.\nTOWNSVILLE\nSUVA\nESPIRITU SANTO\nNOUMEA\nROCKHAMPTON\nNORFOLK ISLAND\nBRISBANE\nclan\nLORD HOWE ISLAND\nSYDNEY O",
      "Cantas Empire Airways",
      "SERVICE\nQantas Empire Airways\nAND ISLANDS AIR\nSERVICES"
    ],
